
To install it do the following:

1) Start Karaf
./karaf clean

2) Install the Jbehave OSGi Services

features:addurl mvn:org.jbehave.osgi/jbehave-osgi-karaf-features/1.0-SNAPSHOT/xml/features
features:install jbehave-osgi


3) After install it you can test with the command:

jbehave:runnerStatus

<-- not working yet -->
4) Install the bundles with the Embedder and Steps classes

osgi:install xxx-snapshot

5) Execute the Jbehave Osgi Story Runner

jbehave:runEmbedder 
